    <section>
        <div class="strategy-block">
            <h2>Sustainable Capital Allocations</h2>
            <p>The transformation of regional utility systems and energy production presents clear structural investment indicators. This mandate systematically targets businesses building the physical foundation of future economic infrastructure.</p>
            
            <ul class="detail-list">
                <li><strong>Renewable Infrastructure Capital:</strong> Identifying asset pools rooted in standard-setting physical grid structures, high-capacity generation facilities, and scalable regional clean utility platforms.</li>
                <li><strong>Electrification Ecosystems:</strong> Investing deliberately in downstream industrial technologies, commercial equipment updates, and grid balancing modernizations.</li>
                <li><strong>Sustainable Enterprise Architecture:</strong> Emphasizing firms implementing industry-leading enterprise cost-reductions through aggressive material and structural resource efficiency models.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="strategy-block" style="background: var(--bg-light); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">A Rigorous Approach to Clean Assets</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0;">Rather than chasing volatile market hype or trends, this portfolio selection framework utilizes data analysis to pinpoint established companies proving real capital efficiency, strict regulatory alignment, and sustainable, long-term balance sheets.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
            <a href="index.html" class="btn-back">&larr; Return to Main Advisory Page</a>
        </div>
    </section>

